{
  "id": "5ca2c3113ccbcd00173db9dd",
  "title": "フレーズベースTF-IDF: 名詞句解析の応用",
  "created": 1554170646,
  "updated": 1596053199,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5ca2c3113ccbcd00173db9dd",
      "text": "フレーズベースTF-IDF: 名詞句解析の応用",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554170646,
      "updated": 1554171340
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2c5cdaff09e0000608aba",
      "text": "\t[フレーズベースTF-IDF]: [名詞句解析]の応用",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554171341,
      "updated": 1554171352
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2c5d9aff09e0000608abb",
      "text": "\t\t[tf-idf]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554171353,
      "updated": 1554171365
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2c5e6aff09e0000608abc",
      "text": "\t\t[キーフレーズ抽出]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554171366,
      "updated": 1554171387
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2c711aff09e0000608abd",
      "text": "\t\t[村脇 有吾] ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554171666,
      "updated": 1554171672
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2c712aff09e0000608abe",
      "text": "  論文抄録\t文書中の重要語の認識は様々な応用の基礎となるタスクである．そうした重要語は，しばしば単語ではなく，単語列からなる．しかし，教師なし手法における state-of-the-art は，単語 TF-IDF の総和によるスコア付けであり，単語列の意味的まとまりを認識しない．そこで，本稿では，名詞句の内部構造解析を応用し，複数の単語からなるフレーズに対して直接 TF-IDF を算出する手法を提案するとともに，その振る舞いを調べる． ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554171666,
      "updated": 1554171666
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2c71faff09e0000608abf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554171680,
      "updated": 1554171681
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2f1b8aff09e0000c36e3a",
      "text": "\t[Conundrums in Unsupervised Keyphrase Extraction]は[TextRank]などの手法よりも単語ベース[TF-IDF]が強いことを示した",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554182584,
      "updated": 1554182765
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2f25faff09e0000c36e3c",
      "text": "\t[単語ベースTF-IDF]はフレーズのスコアを構成単語のTF-IDFの和と定義する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554182752,
      "updated": 1554182784
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2f280aff09e0000c36e3d",
      "text": "\t\tそれに加えて最長名詞句に限定するというヒューリスティクスが無意識に使用されている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554182784,
      "updated": 1554182829
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2f2b0aff09e0000c36e3e",
      "text": "\t\tこれによって[文法性]の問題を回避している",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554182832,
      "updated": 1554182840
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2f1b8aff09e0000c36e3b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554182585,
      "updated": 1554182585
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2f191aff09e0000c36e30",
      "text": "\tunithood",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554182546,
      "updated": 1554182555
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2f19aaff09e0000c36e32",
      "text": "\t\t“the degree of strength or stability of syntagmatic combinations or collocations”",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554182555,
      "updated": 1554182560
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2f300aff09e0000c36e40",
      "text": "\t\t\t単語の連なりがひとかたまりのものとして機能している度合い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554182912,
      "updated": 1554182926
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2f19faff09e0000c36e33",
      "text": "\ttermhood",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554182560,
      "updated": 1554182563
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2f1a2aff09e0000c36e34",
      "text": "\t\t“the degree that a linguistic unit is related to (or more straightforwardly, represents) domain-specific concepts”",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554182563,
      "updated": 1554182565
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2f1a7aff09e0000c36e37",
      "text": "\t\t\t単語の連なりが特定の概念と結びついている度合い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554182567,
      "updated": 1554182945
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2f2f1aff09e0000c36e3f",
      "text": "\t単語ベースTF-IDFは",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554182898,
      "updated": 1554182957
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2f352aff09e0000c36e41",
      "text": "\t\t>[$ \\mathrm{tfidfW}(w) = \\mathrm{tf}(w) \\times log(D/D_w) ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554182995,
      "updated": 1554183842
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2f393aff09e0000c36e42",
      "text": "\t\t\twhere tfは文章中の単語wiの出現頻度、Dは全ての文章数、[$ D_{w_i}]は単語wiを含む文章の数",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554183059,
      "updated": 1554183126
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2f1a7aff09e0000c36e38",
      "text": " \t>[$ \\mathrm{term}(p) = \\sum_{w \\in p} \\mathrm{tfidfW}(w)]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554182568,
      "updated": 1554183794
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2f5c8aff09e0000c36e44",
      "text": " \t\tp: phrase",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554183625,
      "updated": 1554183659
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2f5e5aff09e0000c36e45",
      "text": "\t\t>[$ \\mathrm{unit}(p) = (p\\in\\mathrm{longest(doc)) ? 1 : 0}]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554183653,
      "updated": 1554183797
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2f650aff09e0000c36e46",
      "text": "\t\t\tlongestは最長名詞句",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554183760,
      "updated": 1554183807
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2f67faff09e0000c36e47",
      "text": "\t\t>[$ \\mathrm{tfidf(p)} = \\mathrm{unit}(p) \\times \\mathrm{term}(p)]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554183807,
      "updated": 1554183874
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2f6c6aff09e0000c36e48",
      "text": "\tunitの定義について、最長名詞句であるかどうかだけを使っている。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554183878,
      "updated": 1554183916
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2f6ecaff09e0000c36e4a",
      "text": "\t\t仮に最長名詞句の部分単語列も全て含めた場合",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554183916,
      "updated": 1554183970
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2f6c6aff09e0000c36e49",
      "text": "\t\t\t>[$ \\mathrm{unit}(p) = (p\\in\\mathrm{all(doc)) ? 1 : 0}]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554183878,
      "updated": 1554183975
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2f71aaff09e0000c36e4b",
      "text": "\t\t\tRecallの上界をあげる効果があるが、全体的には精度を悪化させた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554183962,
      "updated": 1554184023
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2f73aaff09e0000c36e4c",
      "text": "\t\t\tこれはつまり、適切でない部分名詞句に対してもunit = 1となっているのがよくない、と考える",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554183994,
      "updated": 1554184065
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2f781aff09e0000c36e4d",
      "text": "\t\t\tそこで部分名詞句に対して適切なスコアをつける",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554184065,
      "updated": 1554184073
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2f789aff09e0000c36e4e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554184073,
      "updated": 1596053199
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2f789aff09e0000c36e4f",
      "text": "このアプローチで、長い文章に対しては精度が向上する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554184073,
      "updated": 1554184957
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2fafdaff09e0000c36e50",
      "text": "短い文章に対しては向上しない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554184957,
      "updated": 1554184963
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca2fb04aff09e0000c36e51",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554184964,
      "updated": 1554184964
    },
